1532
01:53:41,006 --> 01:53:42,406
É Marselha.

1533
01:53:42,827 --> 01:53:44,340
Chama-se Ahmed Jabar.

1534
01:53:44,341 --> 01:53:46,837
O IRC me ajudou a encontrar
a esposa dele, Samia.

1535
01:53:47,359 --> 01:53:49,471
